prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, a funny and lighthearted beach scene. In a beautiful watercolor style with soft edges and blended colors, Lao Lao and Jordan are illustrated as cartoon characters based on the reference photo. Lao Lao is comically trying to drag a giant, oversized inflatable flamingo towards the water, pulling on its neck with a determined and funny expression. Jordan is standing behind her, laughing heartily and holding two tropical drinks with little umbrellas, one of which he is offering to her. They are dressed in beach-appropriate versions of their clothes from the photo: Lao Lao in a light blue rash guard and dark shorts, and Jordan in a tan hoodie over swim trunks. The beach is idyllic with soft white sand, gentle turquoise waves, and a few palm trees. The overall composition is vibrant, joyful, and humorous. Centered in the sky above them is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script. Flat 2D artwork, bright and cheerful color palette.
